    "text": [
        "Dear Manager",
        "",
        "I am a staff in Melbourne Office. I am writing this letter to discuss a training course for my job. Yesterday I found an advertising course in Newspaper, which was so attractive. We may learn how to improve our working efficiency from the course.This sort of training program is one we really want in our practical work. If we can buy this course by company, it would be really appreciated.",
        "",
        "Since we have more staff, we have lost our efficiency in our jobs. Several new colleagues don\u2019t know how to communicate with others. This training will teach us the main skills of working as a team. We need a strong and productive team in this office. Our company can achieve it through participating courses.",
        "",
        "Could you kindly tell the Human resource department to give us the budget of this course? We would like to join this course before the end of this year. I am sure we will enjoy our jobs better than last year.",
        "",
        "Thank you for your consideration.",
        "",
        "Best Regards",
        "",
        "Your Vincent"
